
reset

create cylinder radius 5 height 2
webcut volume 1 with plane yplane offset 4.5 noimprint nomerge 
delete Volume 1
webcut volume all with plane zplane offset 0 noimprint nomerge 
webcut volume all with plane xplane offset -0.5 noimprint nomerge 
delete volume 4 5

imprint all
merge all

surface 22 30 size 0.5
mesh surface 22 30
refine curve 30 numsplit 1 bias 1.0 depth 10 smooth
refine curve 30 numsplit 1 bias 1.0 depth 10 smooth
refine curve 30 numsplit 1 bias 1.0 depth 10 smooth
refine curve 30 numsplit 1 bias 1.0 depth 10 smooth

block 1 surface 22 30
block 1 element type shell4
nodeset 1 curve 28 43
nodeset 2 curve 18 22
nodeset 3 curve 26 40
nodeset 10 surface 22 30
sideset 10 surface 22 30

set large exodus file off
export mesh "porousmesh.exoII"  block all overwrite
